item.obf_query:
t.row_id in (SELECT pacpvd.row_id
FROM sim_pac_pvd pacpvd,
	sim_pia pia,
	sim_processingactivity act
WHERE pia.simpacpia_id=act.row_id
  AND pacpvd.pacpvd_pac_id=pia.simpacpia_id AND pia.row_id=[row_id])

item.obf_query:
t.row_id in (SELECT ent.row_id
FROM gdpr_entity ent 
JOIN gdpr_pac_pvd_ent pacpvdent ON gdpr_pac_pvd_ent_ent_id = ent.row_id
JOIN gdpr_pac_pvd pacpvd ON gdpr_pac_pvd_pvd_id = pacpvd.row_id
JOIN gdpr_processing_activity act ON pacpvd_pac_id = act.row_id
WHERE act.row_id = [row_id])
